snippet.title: Mist and Shadow | Event Trailer
snippet.description:
Natalia is about to embark on a journey to perform a new mission. Can Alucard be her right-hand partner? Will the two work together and complete the mission?

Meanwhile, one of the Pioneers, Sekhet, has arrived in the Land of Dawn. What is her purpose and what will happen to this land? Check the new Tinted Mirage to find out!

Event Time: 03/10/2023
